sequenceDiagram
    participant User as Data Scientist<br/>Web Browser
    participant Router as OpenShift Router<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS1.2+
    participant OAuthProxy as OAuth Proxy<br/>8443/TCP HTTPS TLS1.2+
    participant OAuthServer as OpenShift OAuth Server<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant Backend as Dashboard Backend<br/>8080/TCP HTTP
    participant K8sAPI as Kubernetes API<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS1.2+
    participant Thanos as Thanos Querier<br/>9092/TCP HTTPS TLS1.2+
    participant NotebookCtrl as Notebook Controller<br/>Kubeflow

    Note over User,NotebookCtrl: Flow 1: User Dashboard Access
    User->>Router: GET / <br/>HTTPS Request
    Router->>OAuthProxy: Forward (reencrypt)<br/>Service CA Cert
    OAuthProxy->>OAuthServer: Authenticate User<br/>OAuth 2.0 Flow
    OAuthServer-->>OAuthProxy: OAuth JWT Token
    OAuthProxy->>Backend: Forward Request<br/>Bearer Token
    Backend->>K8sAPI: List Resources<br/>ServiceAccount Token
    K8sAPI-->>Backend: Resource List
    Backend-->>OAuthProxy: Dashboard UI
    OAuthProxy-->>Router: HTTPS Response
    Router-->>User: Dashboard Rendered

    Note over User,NotebookCtrl: Flow 2: Create Notebook
    User->>OAuthProxy: POST /api/notebooks<br/>Bearer Token (OAuth JWT)
    OAuthProxy->>Backend: Forward Request<br/>Bearer Token
    Backend->>K8sAPI: Create Notebook CR<br/>User Token (impersonation)
    K8sAPI-->>Backend: Notebook Created
    Backend-->>OAuthProxy: Success Response
    OAuthProxy-->>User: 201 Created
    NotebookCtrl->>K8sAPI: Watch Notebook CR<br/>ServiceAccount Token
    NotebookCtrl->>K8sAPI: Create StatefulSet<br/>ServiceAccount Token
    K8sAPI-->>NotebookCtrl: StatefulSet Created

    Note over User,NotebookCtrl: Flow 3: Query Metrics
    User->>OAuthProxy: GET /api/prometheus?query=...<br/>Bearer Token
    OAuthProxy->>Backend: Forward Request
    Backend->>Thanos: PromQL Query<br/>ServiceAccount Token
    Thanos-->>Backend: Metric Results
    Backend-->>OAuthProxy: JSON Response
    OAuthProxy-->>User: Metrics Data

    Note over User,NotebookCtrl: Flow 4: Manage Accelerator Profiles
    User->>OAuthProxy: POST /api/accelerator-profiles<br/>Bearer Token
    OAuthProxy->>Backend: Forward Request
    Backend->>K8sAPI: Create AcceleratorProfile CR<br/>User Token
    K8sAPI-->>Backend: AcceleratorProfile Created
    Backend-->>OAuthProxy: Success Response
    OAuthProxy-->>User: Profile Created
